

{"id":2541,"date":"2023-04-18T15:08:30","date_gmt":"2023-04-18T08:08:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=2541"},"modified":"2023-05-18T14:08:56","modified_gmt":"2023-05-18T07:08:56","slug":"nguoi-moi-tap-gym-ngai-den-phong-gym","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/nguoi-moi-tap-gym-ngai-den-phong-gym\/","title":{"rendered":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng Gym v\u00ec 5 l\u00fd do sau \u0111\u00e2y"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym th\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng gym. M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 100 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 gym \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i The New Gym. <em>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4 \u0111\u01a1n! Ng\u1ea1i t\u1eadp gym? S\u1ee3 t\u1eadp gym? L\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp gym? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i t\u1eadp gym?&#8230; l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean google<\/em>. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong ch\u00fang ta, ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. H\u01a1n 50% h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd t\u1eadp gym th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng, v\u00ec The New Gym \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>5 \u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng Gym:<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Tr\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">: <\/span><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong ch\u00fang ta (40%) lo l\u1eafng khi \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp v\u00ec s\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u1eadp gym.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 ti v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">: <\/span><span style=\"color: #212121;\">G\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda n\u1eef gi\u1edbi (45%) cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd lo l\u1eafng trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp xung quanh kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n h\u1ecd (29% nam gi\u1edbi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1).<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">N\u00e2ng t\u1ea1<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">: M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba trong ch\u00fang ta (32%) c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c t\u1eadp squat, h\u00edt x\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u1ef1c. 64% kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c t\u1ea1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u00e0 h\u1ecd n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">M\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">: G\u1ea7n 44% h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">:<\/span> G\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda (48%) h\u1ed9i vi\u00ean cho bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 khi nh\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, v\u00e0 t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 44% khi nh\u1edd nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3732\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3732\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3732 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp gym, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, The New Gym\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/5-dieu-khien-1-nguoi-ngai-den-phong-gym-1-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3732\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng Gym<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><br \/>\nT\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp Gym khi \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c trong ph\u00f2ng Gym:<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">\u00cdt c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t = \u0111\u1ebfn khu v\u1ef1c t\u1eadp t\u1ea1 t\u1ef1 do: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ea1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nh\u1ecbp tim b\u1ea1n t\u0103ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Kh\u00e1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng = s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">H\u1ed9i vi\u00ean c\u00f3 nh\u1ecbp tim v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 (d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ea1y, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e1y). \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u0129 c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp, The New Gym c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng video h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t = y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1: <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp xunh quanh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1eadp, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng cao \u1edf c\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nh\u1ecbp tim.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3730\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3730\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3730 size-full\" style=\"caret-color: #333333; color: #333333; font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi, newbie, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1eadp, The New Gym, t\u1eadp m\u00e1y gym\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tam-ly-cua-nguoi-moi-khi-bat-dau-tap-gym-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3730\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">T\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp Gym<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><br \/>\nT\u1ea1i sao t\u1eadp Gym l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n lo l\u1eafng?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #212121;\">T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1c t\u1ed1t cho ch\u00fang ta, nh\u01b0 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1nh r\u0103ng, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong ch\u00fang ta s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i nh\u01b0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng Gym v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Theo m\u1ed9t nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfn s\u0129 A.S. Margee Kerr, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u2018s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i\u2019 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Pittsburgh, c\u00f4 \u1ea5y gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao t\u1eadp gym kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 v\u00ec \u201c<em>\u0110i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ngo\u00e0i x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang theo t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n khi giao ti\u1ebfp x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng mang theo t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i v\u00e0 lo l\u1eafng<\/em>.\u201d<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Ti\u1ebfn s\u0129 Kerr n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. C\u00f4 \u1ea5y n\u00f3i \u201c<em>L\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng so s\u00e1nh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch xem ch\u00fang ta gi\u1ed1ng nhau, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n hay k\u00e9m h\u01a1n \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng so s\u00e1nh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Khi ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ho\u1eb7c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc, th\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ed9c l\u1ed7 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c, k\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nghi ng\u1edd b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i.<\/em>\u201d<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Ng\u1ecdc Tr\u00e2m, 18 tu\u1ed5i, chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn c\u00f4 lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp: \u201c<em>Vi\u1ec7c \u0111i t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng cho t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 ti, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi \u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, n\u01a1i t\u00f4i so s\u00e1nh c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef kh\u00e1c. N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f4ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo l\u1eafng<\/em>.\u201d<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3728\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3728\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3728 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp gym, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, The New Gym\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/tai-sao-tap-gym-khien-ban-lo-lang-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3728\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 ti, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi \u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, n\u01a1i t\u00f4i so s\u00e1nh c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef kh\u00e1c<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #009fc2; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i t\u1eadp Gym<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #212121;\">Ti\u1ebfn s\u0129 Kerr g\u1ee3i \u00fd nh\u1eefng m\u1eb9o sau \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng khi t\u1eadp gym c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n:<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t<\/strong>. C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i n\u00e0y v\u00ec m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y 5 km hay tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u2013 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 g\u00ec, b\u00e1c s\u0129, v\u1ee3\/ch\u1ed3ng, th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean gia \u0111\u00ecnh, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 B\u1ea0N c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u00f9 l\u1edbn hay nh\u1ecf. <\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>\u0110\u1eebng b\u1ecf qua n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/strong> Ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng k\u00ecm n\u00e9n n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. Trong th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00e0ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng KH\u00d4NG ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho n\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00e1c. <\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>T\u1ef1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.<\/strong> S\u1ee3 h\u00e3i l\u00e0 khi ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7t l\u1ecbch h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, khu v\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy tr\u00ecnh quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3734\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3734\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3734 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2.jpg\" alt=\"t\u1eadp gym, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp gym, The New Gym\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/vuot-qua-noi-so-hai-tap-gym-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3734\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi t\u1eadp Gym<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh mang gi\u00e0y, \u0111eo g\u0103ng tay ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp Gym th\u00ec h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c <\/span><span style=\"color: #009fc2;\"><a style=\"color: #009fc2;\" href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/khu-vuc-tap-luyen-the-new-gym\/\">khu v\u1ef1c t\u1eadp gym<\/a><\/span><span style=\"color: black;\"> ph\u